cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.GT, cs.LG 

This paper discusses the challenges of maintaining a blockchain system and proposes alternative incentive schemes. It touches upon topics such as cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), and machine learning (cs.LG) in its analysis. However, given its focus on the security and decentralization of blockchain, cs.CR and cs.DC are the most likely sub-categories.
